description:
# Dataset:


**Type:** {{dataset.type}}

**Title:** {{dataset.title}}

**Name:** {{dataset.name}}

**Description:** {{dataset.notes}}

{% if dataset.type=='dataset' %}
## Dataset specific fields:


**Maintainer:** {{dataset.maintainer}}

**Maintainer email:** {{dataset.maintainer_email}}

**Author:** {{dataset.author}}

**Author email:** {{dataset.author_email}}

	{% if dataset.extras %}
**Extras:**
		{% for e in dataset.extras %}
		- **{{e.key}}**: _{{e.value}}_
		{% endfor %}
	{% endif %}

**License:** {{dataset.license_title}}

**License url:** {{dataset.license_url}}

{% elif dataset.type=='dcat' %}
## DCAT specific fields:


**Frequency:** {{dataset.frequency}}

**Contact name:** {{dataset.contact_name}}

**Publisher name:** {{dataset.publisher_name}}

**Publisher url:** {{dataset.publisher_url}}

**Provenance:** {{dataset.provenance}}

**Theme:** {{dataset.theme}}

**Spatial:** {{dataset.spatial_text}}

{% endif %}

{% if dataset.version %}
**Version:** {{dataset.version}}
{% endif %}

{% if organization.image_url %}
**Logo:** ![dataset Image]({{organization.image_url}})
{% endif %}

**Page:** [dataset page]({{ckan.base_url}}/{{dataset.type}}/{{dataset.name}})

**State:** {{dataset.state}}

**Private:** {{dataset.private}}

**created on:** {{dataset.metadata_created}}

**changed on:** {{dataset.metadata_modified}}


# Resource:


**Format:** {{resource.format|lower}}

**Title:** {{resource.title}}

**Name:** {{resource.name}}

**Description:** {{resource.description}}

{% if dataset.type=='dataset' %}
	{% if resource.url %}
**URL:** [Resource url]({{resource.url}})
	{% endif %}

{% elif dataset.type=='dcat' %}

## DCAT specific fields:

**License:** {{resource.license}}

**Status:** {{resource.status}}

**Issued**: {{resource.issued}}

**Modified**: {{resource.modified}}

**Languages:**

	{% for lang in resource.language %}
 - {{lang}}
	{% endfor %}

{% endif %}

**Size**: {{resource.size}}

**State:** {{resource.state}}

**MimeType:** {{resource.mimetype}}

**Private:** {{resource.private}}

**created on:** {{resource.created}}

**changed on:** {{resource.last_modified}}


